http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Specialist-consultation-is-now-available-to-all/article14011608.ece

Super-speciality consultation will be available to patients without visiting any multi-speciality or corporate hospitals on out-patient basis. Patients will also be counselled on the best hospital for their specific ailment.City based pulmonologist Anil Kancherla said that Faith Super Specialty Clinics, which was inaugurated on Wednesday, provided out-patient consultation on interventional pulmonology, Cardiac Care, diabetology, snoring and sleep disorders and liver transplant clinics. He said there were could be separate clinics for each of the super speciality services. Faith Speciality Clinics would provide appointments with the required specialists with follow up telephone calls and SMSs to patients who attend the clinics.